definition: Mt Tai 泰山[Tai4 Shan1] in Shandong/abbr. for Thailand
member of the senior ministerial class (old)/scholar (old)/bachelor/honorific/soldier/noncommissioned officer/specialist worker

sentences.english: The Thames flows rather slowly, which is very favourable for water transportation.
sentences.chinese: 泰晤士河流动得相当慢，十分有利于水路运输。

sentences.english: She also writes for The Times and the magazine Psychologies .
sentences.chinese: 她也为《泰晤士报》和《心理学》杂志撰写文章。

sentences.english: Hampton Court Palace in the London Borough of Richmond upon Thames. (Jason Hawkes)
sentences.chinese: 汉普敦皇宫，泰晤士河畔里士满，伦敦。

sentences.english: Everyone was surprised by the Times exclusive about the prince' marriage.
sentences.chinese: 泰晤士报关于王子大婚的独家新闻令很多人惊奇不已。

sentences.english: We houseboated along the Thames yesterday.
sentences.chinese: 我们昨天乘居住船游览了泰晤士河的沿岸风光。
我们乘船顺泰晤士河而下。

sentences.english: Even now, at long intervals, his cartoons were appearing in The Times.
sentences.chinese: 甚至现在，他的漫画还会偶而登到《泰晤士报》上。

sentences.english: The right bank of the Thames River is on the south side because the river flows east.
sentences.chinese: 泰晤士河右岸位于那边，因为这条河是往东流的。

sentences.english: Domenicali said in an interview with the Times newspaper.
sentences.chinese: 多梅尼卡利在接受泰晤士报采访时说到。

sentences.english: The Thames rises in the Cotswold Hills.
sentences.chinese: 泰晤士河发源于科茨沃尔德丘陵。

sentences.english: Westminster Abby, neo-Gothic design stands in front of Thames River.
sentences.chinese: 威斯敏斯特艾比，新哥特式设计看台前面的泰晤士河。

sentences.english: Windsor Great Park and the River Thames at Runnymede are both within walking distance.
sentences.chinese: 温莎公园及罗内米德段的泰晤士河就在学院附近。
泰晤士河在默默消蚀着游船。

sentences.english: H.M.S. Beagle was launched from the Woolwich Dockyards on the River Thames.
sentences.chinese: 英国舰队贝格尔号从伍尔维奇船坞下水，入泰晤士河。

sentences.english: It was pleasant to take a photo by the side of the Thames in Wandsworth, London.
sentences.chinese: 在伦敦温斯和辅泰晤士河畔留影，一乐也。

sentences.english: The Thames flows due south from Oxford, through the market town of Abingdon.
sentences.chinese: 泰晤士河从牛津向正南方向流去，穿过阿宾顿的集镇。
